title: omtivation
pid: fe888556-c0c2-46ea-a7a9-f74e073f3b52
body: |2-
  For any topic,
  there is the branch order that I prefer for myself
  -- presumably familiar with the note or at least the style,
  and probably more interested in open questions than definitions
  -- and there is a different branch order
  that I would curate for others.
